SUBS_OCCS - derived rule, forward substitution at occurrences

SUBS_OCCS: ((int list) * thm) list -> thm -> thm
               li       ti==ui

     t1==u1 ... tn==un      A(t1,...,tn)
    -------------------------------------
	         A(u1,...,un)

Replaces each ti by ui in A, at occurrence numbers specified in the list li.
